 has the ideas and vision to lead our country and restore america as the moral leader in the world. he will always fight to improve the lives of working oklahomans and every working american. </p><p>senator (candidate last) has been a friend to our state and to the causes we hold dear. he has spent more time in oklahoma than any other announced or potential candidates, and he understands and can effectively communicate with our values-driven, populist electorate. during the 2006 election cycle, he worked tirelessly to support our efforts to elect (PARTY NAME) majorities in the state house and senate. he attended fundraisers on behalf of both the house and senate caucuses, profiled our members on his website, and repeatedly offered his personal time and service when it could be of use for fundraising, candidate recruitment and messaging. </p><p>we believe it's time to return the favor to senator (candidate last). not only will we be lending our name to his effort, we will also be working on the ground locally to extend our volunteer organizations to his campaign. </p><p>as the leaders of the (PARTY NAME) party in both houses of the state legislature, we both offer senator (candidate full) our endorsement and our full support. we hope that all of our colleagues in both caucuses join us in supporting senator (candidate last) – the strongest candidate for president in the (PARTY NAME) field. </p><p>sincerely, </p><p>senator mike morgan <br/> president pro tempore </p><p>representative danny morgan<br/> minority leader </p></blockquote></span>



